><a class=\"btns\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/\">Continue reading &#8594;</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/\">WooCommerce Shipping Plugins For Dokan Multivendor Marketplace</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Tarun Sikder\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12280:\"<p>Shipping is one of the essential factors of completing anorder from a <strong>WooCoomerce e-store</strong>. It is the free shipping that attracts customer the most. In many cases, the price attached to shipping deal affects the decision of customer buying that product. If the cost of shipping is higher then it normally <strong>discourages</strong> a customer to get that product from that particular site.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-120036\"></span></p>\n<p>So, therefore, every site requires a firm and convenient shipping policy. And in order to maintain that policy, you need to have comprehensive WooCommerce shipping plugin that would effectively deal your <strong>shipping regularities</strong> better. This would make the customer come to your site over and over again.</p>\n<p>Don\'t you want to improve the WooCommerce shipping <strong>service</strong> of your e-store?</p>\n<p>The answer should be easy right. So here are some of the most efficient WooCommerce shipping plugin for Dokan that can effectively enhance the <strong>shipping service</strong>.</p>\n<h2 class=\"plugin-title\">FedEx WooCommerce Shipping Method Plugin</h2>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"120364\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/fedex-shipping-plugin-image/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1395,445\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"FedEx shipping plugin image\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-300x96.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-1024x327.jpg\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-120364 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image.jpg\" alt=\"FedEx WooCommerce Shipping Plugin\" width=\"1395\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image.jpg 1395w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-300x96.jpg 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-768x245.jpg 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/FedEx-shipping-plugin-image-1024x327.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1395px) 100vw, 1395px\" /></p>\n<p>Well, the plugin is developed by <a href=\"https://www.xadapter.com/?utm_campaign=Dokan-shipping&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_source=wedevs\">XAdapter</a> who is one of the pioneers in the business of creating e-commerce extensions.</p>\n<p>Now we all know how <strong>popular</strong> FedEx is for their shipping services worldwide. But when you want to use the same standard of shipping service with your WooCoomerce site then you need to install and activate this plugin in <strong>DOKAN</strong>.</p>\n<p>This is a plugin that helps process the shipping of products in a WooCommerce based<strong> e-store</strong> through FedEx. The plugin helps its user to get the detail <strong>shipping rates</strong> based on the product\'s weight, location, and other related details.</p>\n<p>This extension to WooCommerce e-store brings an effective yet a <strong>powerful e-commerce shop</strong> to its customers. What makes it even more special is its ability to automatically identify boxes to pack the items and enable tracking.</p>\n<p>It provides multiple vendorsto sell their products through a catalog keeping the facility to ship anywhere through a trusted carrier like FedEx. This plugin is approved and endorsed by <strong>FedEx International (US) Ltd</strong>.</p>\n<h3>How It Works</h3>\n<p>After Installing this plugin with WooCoomerce for Dokan, you will require to input the FedEx account details in order to use your <strong>negotiated</strong> rates. Before placing any order a customer gets to see the FedEx shipping rate based on the product that they have added to the cart.</p>\n<p>Within your WooCommerce order page, you then will have to Pay Postage, Print Label and Generate Tracking info for the goods to be shipped<strong> correctly</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Using the Plugin</h3>\n<p>Here is how you can setup &amp; use this WooCommerce FedEx Shipping plugin for Dokan</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'390\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/pU5D04agO6c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></div>\n<h3>Some Premium features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Print shipping label with postage.</li>\n<li>Automatic shipment tracking while generating the label.</li>\n<li>Weight-based packing &amp; box packing.</li>\n<li>Change the name of shipping services and add handling costs.</li>\n<li>CoD, Third party payer, FedEx LTL Freight &amp; Many more options.</li>\n<li>Timely compatibility updates and bug fixes.</li>\n<li>Premium support!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/fedex-woocommerce-shipping-method//\">Download the WooCommerce FedEx Shipping plugin</a></strong></p>\n<h2 class=\"plugin-title\">DHL WooCommerce Shipping Method Plugin</h2>\n<h2><img data-attachment-id=\"120365\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/dhl-shipping-plugin-image/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1402,455\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"DHL shipping Plugin image\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-300x97.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-1024x332.jpg\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-120365 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image.jpg\" alt=\"DHL WooCommerce Shipping plugin\" width=\"1402\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image.jpg 1402w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-300x97.jpg 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-768x249.jpg 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/DHL-shipping-Plugin-image-1024x332.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1402px) 100vw, 1402px\" /></h2>\n<p>DHL is another popular <strong>shipping service</strong> platform from XAdapter that is loved by millions all over the world. And in the same way as FedEx, this shipping plugin also helps its user to process the shipping of their product in a WooCommerce site <strong>fast &amp; easy.</strong></p>\n<p>This is a plugin allows a customer to buy from multiple vendors in the same order and ship it through <strong>DHL courier service</strong>.</p>\n<p>The plugin helps <strong>automate</strong> the process of shipping providing DHL express service. It shows the accurate rate of shipping that is preset for the different locations before getting to the cart and checkout page in your <strong>WooCommerce store</strong>.</p>\n<p>This process also enables the tracking of shipment including automatic product <strong>packaging</strong> into boxes displaying the print label within WooCommerce. But this plugin only works for countries where the DHL Express service is <strong>available</strong>. And the whole process and this WooCommerce Shipping plugin have been verified &amp; by the <strong>DHL International (UK) Ltd</strong>.</p>\n<h3>How It Works</h3>\n<p>In the same way as FedEx, you need to install and activate the WooCommerce <strong>DHL plugin</strong> for Dokan by putting in the DHL account details, and enabling the <strong>DHL Express/Paket shipping</strong> method for WooCommerce. Since the <strong>shipping rates</strong> change based on the number and type of product you have carted before placing the order, hence it is essential to set the <strong>rate</strong> for shipping accordingly.</p>\n<p>Make necessary<strong> adjustment</strong> in the settings page and then Print Label, Generate Tracking info and Pay Postage within the <strong>WooCommerce order page</strong>. This will let you ship the product to the <strong>desired destination</strong> without any trouble.</p>\n<h3>Using the plugin</h3>\n<div class=\"porto-separator tall\">\n<div class=\"divider align_center divider-primary\">Here is how you can setup &amp; use the WooCommerce DHL Express plugin for Dokan.</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'390\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/PBCx1qLIccI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></div>\n<h3>Some Premium Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Print shipping label with Postage.</li>\n<li>Return Label.</li>\n<li>Commercial Invoice.</li>\n<li>Archive Air Waybill.</li>\n<li>Create &amp; Delete shipments in Bulk.</li>\n<li>Use the paperless trade feature and get a commercial invoice from DHL.</li>\n<li>Auto Shipment Tracking: Tracking info will be available to the customer while generating the label.</li>\n<li>Box packing with DHL boxes and Custom boxes.</li>\n<li>Enable/disable, edit the names of services and add handling costs to shipping services.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/dhl-woocommerce-shipping-method/\">Download the WooCommerce DHL Shipping plugin</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Observations</h3>\n<p>If you are selling physical goods then shipping is one of the<strong> basic necessity</strong> in your business plan. Keeping the cost of shipping at a reasonable range would<strong> boost up</strong> your conversion for sure. Not just that it would also change the <strong>perception</strong> of your e-store if you <strong>momentarily</strong> take off the burden of shipping cost from customers. It will definitely<strong>increase</strong> the number of order from your e-shop.</p>\n<h2>Concluding Words</h2>\n<p>If you are using WooCommerce with Dokan then you will definitely find this post<strong> useful</strong>. Our sole intention of this write up was to inform you about the<strong> necessity</strong> and use case of a <strong>powerful shipping plugin</strong> for Dokan to improve your WooCommerce website performance.</p>\n<p>So we hope you have <strong>enjoyed</strong> this post and found the use case of these valid WooCoommece shipping plugin for Dokan useful in some way.</p>\n<p>And if you are using WordPress and thinking about starting up a <strong>multivendor store</strong> on your own, then you may want to &#8211;</p>\n<p><strong><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"http://dokandemo.wedevs.com/my-account/\">Try The Dokan Multivendor Marketplace Demo</a></strong></p>\n<p>Do leave a comment if you have any <strong>queries</strong> regarding these shipping plugins for<strong> Dokan</strong>. We would be more than happy to assist you any way possible.</p>\n\n<div style=\"display: block !important; margin:0 !important; padding: 0 !important\" id=\"wpsclp_locker_post_end_element\"></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/\">WooCommerce Shipping Plugins For Dokan Multivendor Marketplace</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://wedevs.com/120036/woocommerce-shipping-plugin-for-dokan/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"120036\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"Dokan is Getting More Affordable: Price Reduction &amp; Changes in Packages\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://wedevs.com/103718/dokan-price-reduction-changes-packages/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://wedevs.com/103718/dokan-price-reduction-changes-packages/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 23 Nov 2017 11:05:27 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Dokan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Dokan Package\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Dokan Pricing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Featured\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Multivendor Marketplace\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://wedevs.com/?p=103718\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:472:\"<p>Marketplaces are changing, so is Dokan Multivendor. We are reducing Dokan Pro entry package price and bringing entirely new pricing where you get addons pre-activated for free depending on your package.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/103718/dokan-price-reduction-changes-packages/\">Dokan is Getting More Affordable: Price Reduction &#038; Changes in Packages</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"M Asif Rahman\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18472:\"<p>Back in the days when we released the first version of <strong>Dokan</strong>, it was actually a <strong>Premium Theme</strong>. If you know Dokan only for a year or two, I know how ridiculousit sounds. But, that\'s how it all got started. Soon we realized Dokan could do more, and to be able to grow we need to change dramatically, we evolved to a fully functional<strong>Plugin</strong>. Later we created many addons that adds even more functionality. Currently, there are over 18 official and 3rd-party addons. But the current process is &#8211; you have to buy a Dokan Pro license and buy Addons separately. We are changing this to help you, the Dokan user (the most important segment) grow, at the same time, we (weDevs) could push Dokan to new heights.</p>\n<h2><strong>Dokan Pricing Before?</strong></h2>\n<p>Currently, there is a free core version of Dokan available at WordPress.org, that will remain the same. You get all the awesome feature, which is even comparable with other premium solution (you could look at <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/dokan/compare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this comparison</a> if you have not yet). If you want to upgrade now you have this packages for you to upgrade &#8211;</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"103727\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/103718/dokan-price-reduction-changes-packages/dokan-old-packages/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages.png\" data-orig-size=\"1330,665\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dokan Old Packages\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages-300x150.png\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages-1024x512.png\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103727\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1330\" height=\"665\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages.png 1330w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages-300x150.png 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages-768x384.png 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages-1024x512.png 1024w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Old-Packages-600x300.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1330px) 100vw, 1330px\" /></p>\n<p>And after that, if you want to have more feature you could have purchased any or all of the addons below &#8211;</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"103728\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/103718/dokan-price-reduction-changes-packages/dokan-addons/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons.png\" data-orig-size=\"1021,774\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dokan Addons\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons-300x227.png\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons.png\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103728\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1021\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons.png 1021w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons-300x227.png 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons-768x582.png 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-Addons-600x455.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1021px) 100vw, 1021px\" /></p>\n<h2><strong>What Is Changing?</strong></h2>\n<p>In short, we are combining Dokan Pro and our addons. So, now you don\'t have to buy Dokan Pro &amp; Addons separately, we are packaging it together. And our pricing is getting simpler as well. <strong>And the entry package in Dokan Pro is now cheaper, and we are announcing Live Chat support forthe Enterprise Package.</strong></p>\n<h2>Dokan is Now More Affordable Than Ever Before!</h2>\n<p>It\'s like a present from Santa before the Christmas even started!</p>\n<p>Yeah, now Dokan is available at a reduced price. It\'s not an offer! From now on, you can buy Dokan Multivendor Marketplace Plugin for <strong>only $149</strong>. This means we have reduced the price by <strong>$50</strong>! Here are the new Pricing and Packages at a glimpse &#8211;</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"103825\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/103718/dokan-price-reduction-changes-packages/dokan-new-package-pricing-list/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list.png\" data-orig-size=\"1422,647\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"dokan-new-package-pricing-list\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list-300x136.png\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list-1024x466.png\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103825\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1422\" height=\"647\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list.png 1422w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list-300x136.png 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list-768x349.png 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list-1024x466.png 1024w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-package-pricing-list-600x273.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1422px) 100vw, 1422px\" /></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wedevs.com/dokan/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Check the new Pricing!</strong></a></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Not only that, we have also added all our existing add-ons as modules in premium packs so that you get what you need at a reasonable price. We are making things easier for you and helping you to decide what you really need.</p>\n<p>You don\'t have to worry about premium add-ons and calculate how much it will cost after you have bought the Pro plugin for $199.</p>\n<h3>Starter &amp; Professional Package</h3>\n<p>The Starter package is now only $149 and it provides you all the features that were available on previous Dokan 1 site license. If you spend $100 more, you get amazing useful modules with the Professional package &#8211;</p>\n<p>Professional package gives you handy modules to &#8211;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Vendor Review worth $4</strong>9:Manage the way your vendors interact with the customers</li>\n<li><strong>Store Support worth $39:</strong>Provide support to each user</li>\n<li><strong>Seller Verification worth $39:</strong> Verify real vendors</li>\n<li><strong>PayPal Adaptive worth $49:</strong> Most popular payment gateway</li>\n<li><strong>Stripe Connect worth $49:</strong> Stripe integration for your marketplace</li>\n<li><strong>Subscriptions worth $39:</strong>Create subscription system for your vendors</li>\n<li><strong>AJAX Live Search worth $19:</strong>Advanced search features</li>\n</ul>\n<p>As you can see, all these awesome modules are worth $283 and it saves you $183!</p>\n<h3>Business &amp; Enterprise Package</h3>\n<p>Here at weDevs, we want our users to get all the important features at a reasonable price. Thus, we have decided to give whats best for you.</p>\n<p>So, we have curated the whole pricing and package to provide differenttypes of solutions to different types of users. Our Free plugins provide you all the basic features that you need to run a multivendor marketplace.</p>\n<p>The Starter &amp; Professional package gives you advanced features that make your multivendor marketplace whole. You get amazing features to grow your business and earn the way you want.</p>\n<p>With the Business package, you get even more powerful modules like WooCommerce Booking Integration,Seller Vacation, Product Enquiry, Export-Import, Auction Support. Most importantly, you get &#8211;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1-hour basic installation of Dokan to your website</li>\n<li>1-hour theme compatibility support</li>\n<li>Premium support from our excellent support team</li>\n<li>Live Chat etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>So, no more Addons?</h2>\n<p>No, we won\'t sale addons separately, now we call those modules, depending on the package you purchase, you will get those modules pre-activated, in the new Module menu. You could activate and deactivate depending on your use.</p>\n<h2>What Happens to theExisting Add-on Users?</h2>\n<p>It will keep working as it should, but you will have the choice to upgrade to Higher Pro package with 50% discount if you have an active license for Dokan Pro.</p>\n<h2>Why are We Doing this?</h2>\n<p>As I explained at the beginning Dokan is growing, so as the Marketplace ecosystem. We did not create all of our addons in one day, it was created over the year, and the way we see it extends Dokan functionality to a height that we are very proud of. But as you have to buy each and every addons separately, and it\'s very much possible that you don\'t even know that Dokan offers a function, which costs maybe just $19 bucks. We feel here pricing should not be a burden, the function discovery process should have been more straightforward. If Dokan has a certain feature, we want our user to use that, we know from our user that those features are helpful, the extra addon should not bother now, now you have very easier choice, you buy once, pay once and you have access to all the functionalities that are useful to you for a whole year.</p>\n<h2>What\'s New in Dokan Multivendor V 2.7.0</h2>\n<h3>Introducing All New Modules for Dokan</h3>\n<p>Say bye bye to previous add-ons, which were very difficult to manage. From our new update, we are going to transform all our add-ons into modules. Guess what, you will be able to manage all of them from a single place. So, we have added a new menu called &#8216;Modules\' and removed the old &#8216;Add-ons\' menu. This is how the new page looks like.</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"103707\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/dokan-new-modules-page/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page.png\" data-orig-size=\"1331,734\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"dokan-new-modules-page\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page-300x165.png\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page-1024x565.png\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103707\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1331\" height=\"734\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page.png 1331w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page-300x165.png 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page-768x424.png 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page-1024x565.png 1024w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-modules-page-600x331.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1331px) 100vw, 1331px\" /></p>\n<p>You get all the previous add-ons as modules. They will be available on a single page so its easier for you to manage. This means you don\'t have to install separate plugins to use the features. Now, you can simply click on a toggle button and activate or deactivate any module you want! Neat, right? ?</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"103708\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/dokan-new-module-activation-deactivation/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-new-module-activation-deactivation.gif\" data-orig-size=\"1282,720\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dokan new module activation deactivation\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-new-module-activation-deactivation-300x168.gif\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-new-module-activation-deactivation-1024x575.gif\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103708\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Dokan-new-module-activation-deactivation.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1282\" height=\"720\" /></p>\n<h3>Automatic Updates for Modules</h3>\n<p>Previously, you didn\'t get a live update for any of the Dokan add-ons. Now, you can manage them from a single place as well as get live updates directly with Dokan plugin. So, no more manual updates! You don\'t have to download each add-ons and install them separately every time you get an update.</p>\n<h3>Interactive Settings Page to Manage it All</h3>\n<p>Dokan now has better and improved settings page where you can easily configure everything for your Dokan Multivendor.</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"103717\" data-permalink=\"https://wedevs.com/dokan-new-settings-page/\" data-orig-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page.png\" data-orig-size=\"1292,723\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"dokan-new-settings-page\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page-300x168.png\" data-large-file=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page-1024x573.png\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-103717\" src=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1292\" height=\"723\" srcset=\"https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page.png 1292w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page-300x168.png 300w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page-768x430.png 768w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page-1024x573.png 1024w, https://wedevs.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dokan-new-settings-page-600x336.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1292px) 100vw, 1292px\" /></p>\n<h2>Our Advise to You</h2>\n<p>Keeping your WordPress site updated is very important. The latest version of <strong>WordPress 4.9</strong> brings so many useful features, you could check the all amazing feature in <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/102421/wordpress-4-9-features/\">this article</a>. And if you want to know in details why you should always keep your Dokan Store updated and use the latest version of WooCommerce, you should check <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/98595/keep-wordpress-store-updated/\">this article</a>.</p>\n<p>If you are currently using Dokan Pro $199 package with 2 paid addons and wondering what will happen to you, we will update you to Professional Package for free, just <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/account/create-new-ticket/\">contact our support</a>. In the same way, if you are an existing paid user with an active license and using any paid addons, please also<a href=\"https://wedevs.com/account/create-new-ticket/\">contact</a> our support.</p>\n<p>If you are were using Dokan Lite Free version with any addon it will continue to work, all free addons will keep working. The only thing you won\'t be able to do is buy just one addon anymore. If you are already using any Premium Addon with our Lite version, you won\'t get any update, but our addon update process was manual before anyway. And we will offer 50% discount to any free version user with any paid extension or expired license user to upgrade to desired Pro package.</p>\n<p>Again we want to express our gratitude to all existing Dokan user, and we promise Dokan will grow even faster from now on, we are very excited about many new features we are currently working on, and this new structure will help us grow faster.</p>\n\n<div style=\"display: block !important; margin:0 !important; padding: 0 !important\" id=\"wpsclp_locker_post_end_element\"></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/103718/dokan-price-reduction-changes-packages/\">Dokan is Getting More Affordable: Price Reduction &#038; Changes in Packages</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a: